  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Research, biostatistics, statistics, and data analytics support for public health and development economics work</h2>
      <p>I help NGOs, public health programs, academic teams, and government institutions generate evidence, analyze data, and improve decisions.</p>
      <a href="#contact" class="btn">Contact Me</a>
