          <p>Descriptive, inferential, and advanced statistical analysis for research and decision-making.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Research Support</h3>
          <p>Study design, proposal writing, questionnaire design, and methodology support.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Monitoring & Evaluation</h3>
          <p>Indicator tracking, reporting, program evaluation, and evidence generation.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
